title: Best and worst signings
itunes:title: Best and worst signings
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- breaks down all the latest free agency happenings, including DeMarco Murray's move to the Philadelphia Eagles. Who made the most sensible signings? Which team will regret dropping the big bucks? Tune into the latest "Around the NFL Podcast" to find out.
